    - target: {fileID: 2113875699234556495, guid: 18470d71939382448be2ecd06efa9662,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "<size=42><b>Scrolling Object Collection</b></size>\r\n\nThis example
        scene demonstrates different types of scroll interaction with a ScrolingObjectCollection
        component. \n\nThis control enables the scrolling of 3D content through a
        contained viewable area. The frame movement can be triggered by click and
        drag with a controller or by discrete pagination."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
